**Installing and configuring DHCP server and assign IP**

1) **Make Connections.**  
2) **Server \-\>	Enable DHCP**

   **Set IP configuration**

			**IPV4 Address : 10.0.0.1**  
			**Default Gateway : 10.0.0.2**  
			**DNS IP : 10.0.0.1![][image1]**

3) **Server \-\> Services \-\> DHCP :**

   	**Default Gateway : 10.0.0.2**

   	**DNS server : 10.0.0.1**

   	**Starting IP: 10 \- 0 \- 0 \- 3**

   **Save**

**![][image2]**

4) **PC \-\> IP Configuration set DHCP ![][image3]**  
5) **Automatically Assign IP addresses to client machines using dhcp server**

6) **Test by sending Messages**
